Add simm command tools only for maintainence usage.

Tool Name Convention:
  simm_xxx_admin

  e.g. global flags admin tool, use simm_flags_admin.cc as source code file name, and
  cmake & make will output simm_flags_admin binary to related directory

  simm_xxx_bench
  e.g. io bench tool to test simm performance, including io latency, iops, throughput